    "7302504": {
        "Desc": "Enter Vanarana",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh, an Aranara..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "Eek! Don't capture me, I'll give Nara \"tracer\"..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What's a \"tracer\"? Anyway, we won't capture you! Don't be afraid!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#This is Paimon, and {M#he}{F#she} is {NICKNAME}. We're good Nara! What's your name?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "Oh... You're good Nara, great. Hmm, it was Arana who taught you that tune, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "I'm Arama. Arana may trust both of you, but everyone here is very scared seeing Nara in Vanarana."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Aren't you afraid as well?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "I was afraid. But the Golden Nara has been to many places. The tiny dandelions and spores with you are all saying that you are a very, very good Nara."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Whoa, Aranara can communicate with plants, even spores?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Spores aren't plants..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "#Nara {NICKNAME} understands, Paimon is wrong. If you say that loudly in the forest, plants will be sad, and spores will be angry and might even turn into Fungi."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "That's convenient!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "How strange. Spores are not plants. If you say that loudly in the forest, plants will be sad, and spores will be angry and might even turn into Fungi."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ugh! Let's not fuss over the details, shall we?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Anyway, is this Vanarana? It feels so similar to the place where we found the treasure, but it is slightly different. It does have a huge rock house, but..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Is this Vanarana?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmm... It feels so similar to the place where we found the treasure, but it is slightly different. It does have a huge rock house, but..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Feeling a little disappointed?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "It isn't what Paimon expected! Paimon thought Vanarana would be a lively Aranara village where everyone would be dancing Aranara dances, eating Aranara food, completing Aranara commissions..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "And an Aranara Katheryne?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "And an Aranara souvenir shop?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "And an Aranara outrider..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "...Paimon's thoughts didn't run that wild!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "#Everyone's in Vanarana, but because everyone's afraid, we still can't let both of you inside, even if Nara {NICKNAME} is golden."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Golden...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What about silver? Is silver bad?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "Silver, just like the moon. Very good, very good."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hee-hee... So here isn't Vanarana?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Golden? Is it rare?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What about silver? Is silver rare?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "Silver, just like the moon. Very good, very good."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hee-hee... So here isn't Vanarana?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Isn't here Vanarana?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "This isn't Vanarana. Ah, actually... This is Vanarana, but not the real Vanarana."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "So is it Vanarana or not..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "If you help Aranara, everyone won't be afraid, and you can enter the real Vanarana. Come with me, help Aranara and get the \"tracer.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon gets it now! You mean \"treasure\"! Sure, we'll help you!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
