    "7307013": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Arama",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Is this... the Vasara Tree? Doesn't seem as lively as Paimon imagined..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "Yes, Aramaha resisted very hard, and kept Marana under control to the side. If not, the nearby forest would have become even more terrible."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "All the leaves would fall and rot on the ground. The mushrooms would all become angry Fungi, and the birds and beasts would also lie down and return to the ground, leaving only hard white things behind."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Sounds really scary..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "#Yes, but thanks to Nara {NICKNAME} and Paimon, Marana has become a lot less troubling!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "If it were just Arama alone, it wouldn't have worked at all. I am too young and don't have many memories, so I am not as powerful as other Aranara."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "#But with memories of adventuring together with Nara {NICKNAME} and Paimon, my powers will grow!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "The same goes for us."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yeah! Friends go on adventures together! That's the spirit!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What's next?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "First, we must enter his dream to destroy Marana's lingering influence."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wait a second... When you say \"his dream,\" you mean that of the Vasara Tree?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "That's right. If you are ready, reach out your hand and enter his dream..."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
