    "7307411": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Arama",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Is this... the Vasara Tree? Doesn't seem as lively as Paimon imagined..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "It must've been corroded by Marana... I'm so sorry, Arayama. We never realized that Marana's corruption had even reached here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "When I was a teeny tiny seed, I heard stories about Aramuhukunda, Arayama, and Araji."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "Arayama didn't really like Nara, so he created the phantasmal barrier. He was happy to see the Nara's frustrated faces. But there was one Nara who saw through his Ararakalari."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "No matter how hard he tried, that Nara always found a way to break through. Then they slowly became friends."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Well, that's how some friendships form... What happened to Arayama in the end?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "At the end of the story, a great catastrophe occurred. He protected a lot of Aranara and Nara."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "Ah! No wonder his song could disperse all those illusions. It's because their game has ended."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "How can we get the Vasoma Fruit?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "First, we must enter his dream to destroy Marana's lingering influence."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wait a second... When you say \"his dream,\" you mean that of the Vasara Tree?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "That's right. If you are ready, reach out your hand and enter his dream..."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7307415": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Arama and enter the Vasara Tree's dream",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "(Reach your hand out to the Vasara Tree...)"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7307417": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Arama and enter the Vasara Tree's dream",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So this is..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "Yes. This is a Vasoma Fruit."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "It is the accumulation of the dreams and memories gathered by the Vasara Tree. It's a precious fruit that can help us restore our strength."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "A large amount of energy must be consumed for the Ashvattha Tree to produce a Bija. That is why we must offer Vasoma Fruits."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "#Keep the Vasoma Fruit safe, Nara {NICKNAME}!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmm. You know what? Let's teach Arama the meaning of \"treasure\"!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Now then! \"Treasure\" refers to something very precious. This Vasoma Fruit contains lots of dreams and memories, and it can restore an Aranara's power. That makes it pretty rare and amazing, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "For things like Vasoma Fruits that are rare and precious, we call them \"treasure\"!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "Ah, so this is what treasure means... I got it! Thank you, Paimon!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "So, what's next?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmm... Araja said that we'll need more than one Vasoma Fruit. That means we need to find other Ashvattha's Concourses, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Thanks, Paimon!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What are you thanking Paimon for...? Anyway, Araja said that we'll need more than one Vasoma Fruit. That means we need to find other Ashvattha's Concourses, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "#That's right. I'll do my best to find them! So long, Nara {NICKNAME} and Paimon!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "See you later, Arama!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
